#org @noRoom
textcolor 0x0
msgbox @noRoomTalk 0x6
release
end

#org @itemGet
fanfare 0x101
textcolor 0x2
preparemsg @itemMsg
waitmsg
waitfanfare
msgbox @putAway MSG_KEEPOPEN
return

#org @itemCollect
pause 0x8
msgbox @hangOn 0x6
applymovement SELLER @walk1
waitmovement 0x0
pause 0x10
spriteface ASSISTANT FACE_UP
applymovement ASSISTANT @stepU
waitmovement 0x0
applymovement ASSISTANT @faceBack
applymovement SELLER @walk2
waitmovement 0x0
pause 0x10
msgbox @itemTalk 0x6
return

#org @noMoreRewards
msgbox @noMoreTalk 0x6
release
end

#org @introTalk
= Hey there, man. Listen up!\nYou've come to the right place.\pWe're tired of seeing all of these\nRockets cowering in fear at\lLance's new anti-crime measures,\lgoing all soft and refraining from\lstealing Pokémon just so people on\lthe street won't be mean to them.\pWe say screw that! Let's bring\nTeam Rocket back to its roots!\pThat's why we're setting up shop\nhere-- to reward the biggest and\lbaddest Rockets for keeping our\lname notorious throughout Kanto!\pThe higher the bounty on your\nhead, the greater the reward we'll\lgive you!

#org @introTalk2
= Well, what's your name?\c\h08ó\n[.][player]?\pWe'll look you up in the police\nregistry to see if you're worthy\lof our respect.

#org @regularTalk
= Hey, man! Been stealing a lot of\ninnocent Trainers' Pokémon lately?\p[.]\c\h08ó\n[player], is it? Let me see[.]

#org @gt60talk
= Holy moly!\c\h08ó\n[$][buffer1],000?!\p[.]\c\h08ó\nDude, I'm[.] humbled.\pYou've got to be one of the most\nvaluable Rockets we've got, man[.]\pAs thanks for your bringing so\nmuch notoriety back to Team\lRocket, we'll give you our most\lprized possession.\pI know it couldn't be in better\nhands!

#org @gt40talk
= Well, I'll be damned!\c\h08ó\n[$][buffer1],000? Wow.\pDude, you've got to be one of the\nmost badass people we've got!\pWoe is the poor Trainer who dares\nmess with you, my man!\pThanks for helping us bring back\nTeam Rocket's reputation.

#org @gt20talk
= Oh, [$][buffer1],000!\c\h08ó\nI'm impressed.\pYou really don't give a flying\nyou-know-what, do you?\pHaha!\nI like you, bud.\pWe need more tough guys like you\naround here.

#org @gt10talk
= Hmmm[.] [$][buffer1],000.\c\h08ó\nThat's respectable.\pYou're no crazy renegade, but\nyou're on the right track!\pKeep it up, dude, and don't let\nnobody fool you with childish\ldelusions of morality!\pMight is right in the gangster\ngame, ya hear?

#org @notBadTalk
= Hmm[.] [$][buffer1],000?\c\h08ó\pWell, that's hardly anything to\nbrag about.\pI say quit being a little wussy\nand get stealing some more, pal!\pWe'll have some goodies for you\nhere if you do.

#org @innocentTalk
= What?\c\h08ó But there's no bounty on\nyour head at all!\pWhat's the matter, little buddy?\nScared of the cops?\c\h08ó Wah-wah.\pGeez, quit wasting our time and\nget stealing, man! C'mon!

